nodes.description: This node is responsible for generating the initial essay based on the user's request.
This node is responsible for reflecting on the generated essay and providing critique and recommendations.
This node represents the end of the process after a certain number of iterations or when the final essay is deemed good enough.

edges.condition: After generating the essay, transition to reflection for critique and recommendations.
After reflecting, go back to generate to improve the essay based on the feedback.
If the reflection indicates that the essay is good enough or after a set number of iterations, transition to the end node.
